      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this stunning, showroom-quality vehicle! It is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every detail, from the flawless paint to the immaculate interior, reflects the highest level of care. This is a rare opportunity to own a car that is practically brand new!",
