      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, appearing almost as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no visible imperfections, while the interior is spotless, showing virtually no signs of use. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, ensuring it drives as perfectly as it looks. A buyer can expect a collector-quality vehicle that requires absolutely no additional work or care.",
