    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideal for a mechanic or as a parts donor. The engine has major issues, frequently failing to start and stalling at idle, and the transmission exhibits severe slipping in most gears. Both the exterior and interior show significant wear and tear, including body rust and torn upholstery. Please expect to tow this vehicle away, as it is not currently roadworthy.",
